graph TB
    %% Actors
    Admin([Admin])
    Dosen([Dosen])
    Guest([Guest])

    %% Use Cases - Authentication
    Login[Login System]
    Register[Register Dosen]
    EmailVerif[Email Verification]
    ForgotPass[Forgot Password]
    Logout[Logout]
    
    %% Use Cases - Profile Management
    EditProfile[Edit Profile]
    ChangePassword[Change Password]
    DeleteAccount[Delete Account]

    %% Supporting Use Cases for Include Relationships
    ValidateCredentials[Validate Credentials]
    ValidateRegistration[Validate Registration Data]
    SendEmailVerification[Send Email Verification]
    SendResetLink[Send Reset Password Link]
    ResetPassword[Reset Password]
    ValidateOldPassword[Validate Old Password]
    UpdateProfileData[Update Profile Data]
    SendAccountDeletionEmail[Send Account Deletion Email]

    %% Supporting Use Cases for Extend Relationships
    RememberMe[Remember Me]
    UploadProfilePhoto[Upload Profile Photo]
    ConfirmAccountDeletion[Confirm Account Deletion]

    %% Admin Connections
    Admin --> Login
    Admin --> Logout
    Admin --> EditProfile
    Admin --> ChangePassword

    %% Dosen Connections
    Dosen --> Login
    Dosen --> Register
    Dosen --> EmailVerif
    Dosen --> ForgotPass
    Dosen --> Logout
    Dosen --> EditProfile
    Dosen --> ChangePassword
    Dosen --> DeleteAccount

    %% Guest Connections
    Guest --> Register
    Guest --> Login
    Guest --> ForgotPass

    %% Include Relationships (mandatory)
    Login -.->|include| ValidateCredentials
    Register -.->|include| ValidateRegistration
    Register -.->|include| SendEmailVerification
    ForgotPass -.->|include| SendResetLink
    ForgotPass -.->|include| ResetPassword
    ChangePassword -.->|include| ValidateOldPassword
    EditProfile -.->|include| UpdateProfileData
    DeleteAccount -.->|include| SendAccountDeletionEmail

    %% Extend Relationships (optional/conditional)
    RememberMe -.->|extend| Login
    UploadProfilePhoto -.->|extend| Register
    UploadProfilePhoto -.->|extend| EditProfile
    ConfirmAccountDeletion -.->|extend| DeleteAccount

